pan><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">: [</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-6 grvsc-tL6fl1-8\">&quot;${file}&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">],</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">      </span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-4 grvsc-tL6fl1-9\">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">: {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">        </span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-4 grvsc-tL6fl1-9\">&quot;kind&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-6 grvsc-tL6fl1-8\">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">        </span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-4 grvsc-tL6fl1-9\">&quot;isDefault&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">: </span><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-7 grvsc-tL6fl1-4\">true</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">      }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">    }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">  ]</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tJZ19p-1 grvsc-tL6fl1-1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>7행에 <code>command</code>는 자신이 Lua 프로그램의 위치를 써주면 됩니다.\r\n물론 아까 <code>Path</code>를 설정했지만 오류가 날 수 도 있기 때문에 이렇게 해주는 것이 좋습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"마무리\" style=\"position:relative;\">마무리<a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"마무리 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"fals